metadata.description:
"All you left me with are these memories, that I'm drowning out with this Hennessy, just to hide the fact that I'm too afraid to move on."

The song is written like a sad break up song but for me it's a lot deeper than that. For me it isn't really about a relationship at all.
I could bore you with the sad details but it's pretty personal. If you enjoy the song and are curious,  feel free to reach out to me on Twitter and I'd love to talk about it.
